	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Detroit</placeName> <date>Novemb 13&#47;51</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philad.</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your favor of the <date>28th</date> ult and also<lb/> your <sic>valueable</sic> magazine came to hand<lb/> We enclose &#36;3 for our subscription &#38; &#36;3 for<lb/> <persName>C &#38; C E Baessler</persName> <placeName>Detroit</placeName> to whose address<lb/> you will also please to send the Occident</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">We shall when an opportunity<lb/> offers gladly speak to our friends of the<lb/> Occident &#38; your translated bible &#38; solicit<lb/> subscription.</p>
				<p>As regards our congregation here&#44; it counts<lb/> only a very limited number of members<lb/> &#38; is of a quite recent organization.<lb/>  Several men having moved here with their<lb/> <del>their</del> families &#40;sometime last year&#41; the<lb/> total want of all opportunities for religious<lb/> instruction of their children was severely<lb/> felt especially as their business called<lb/> them away from home most of the time.<lb/>  Subsequently at a meeting called among<lb/> those few <add>Hebrew</add> residing here &#40;12 members&#41;<lb/> it was resolved to call a teacher &#38; shochet<lb/> &#38; also to buy a plot of land for a <sic>burrying</sic><lb/> ground.  The incident expenses though con&#44;<lb/>siderable were contributed with a good<lb/> deal of liberality &#38; the above resolution carved out.<lb/>  The number of our member has since then<lb/> augmented to 18.</p>
				<p>The prospects for erection of a synagogue are<lb/> rather remote yet being so few in number<lb/> it will have to be differed to a <sic>latter</sic></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>and more auspicious period.<lb/>  Should on your contemplated western tour<lb/> you happen to visit <placeName>Detroit</placeName> allow us<lb/> to invite you to call on us.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">We shall cheerfully <sic>attent</sic> to any thing that<lb/> might be of service to your cause.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Wishing you health &#38; happiness</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">We remain Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName>S Freedman &#38; Bros</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">by <persName role="author">Joseph Freedman</persName></p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Penn</placeName></p>
				<p>Paid</p>
		</body>
